{"tid":1198793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國刑法：散布謠言可判7年","createTime":"2019-06-10T10:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:39:40.000Z","uid":12919,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"474203c1aae4d655be558a9b885e05f8129e2b83","tid":1198793,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:26:52.000Z","msg":"編造虛假的險情、疫情、災情、警情，在信息網絡或者其他媒體上傳播，或者明知是上述虛假信息，故意在信息網絡或者其他媒體上傳播，嚴重擾亂社會秩序的，處三年以下有期徒刑、拘役或者管制；造成嚴重後果的，處三年以上七年以下有期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20151028-dailynews-criminal-law/?fbclid=IwAR1ZIfpsozOJmWSCcxCAqTrO5Hfbjow6vrWZ8EYJQ9UM_rmKDJohuJcRSW0&amp;utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20151028-dailynews-criminal-law%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1ZIfpsozOJmWSCcxCAqTrO5Hfbjow6vrWZ8EYJQ9UM_rmKDJohuJcRSW0%26utm_medium%3Dcopy&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCMv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=cdca49ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20151028-dailynews-criminal-law/?fbclid=IwAR1ZIfpsozOJmWSCcxCAqTrO5Hfbjow6vrWZ8EYJQ9UM_rmKDJohuJcRSW0&amp;utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超：<br />\n《逃犯條例》修訂方案將罪行引渡門檻提高至可判最高刑期七年或以上"},{"pid":"6c36fc15822914c152b740769d756fa71da2f001","tid":1198793,"uid":12919,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"你班on9仲話咩無犯法怕咩俾人修例<br />\n<br />\n你而家隨時講句野都話散布謠言<br />\n<br />\n仲有你屋企人最撚鐘意用既微信，講兩句野就可以捉返大陸坐呀"},{"pid":"c44bb5792dedef33370d79bec30408d27b904de8","tid":1198793,"uid":12919,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"仲想扮無記性呀？<br />\n<br />\n大陸毒奶粉單野咪就係講真野，就俾人話散布謠言拉9左好多人"},{"pid":"943e9947664997fa65f1ebf30101f067d4c8b0c7","tid":1198793,"uid":12919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"到呢家仲諗住自己唔會犯法被判七年呀？<br />\n<br />\n上連登留言俾三毛篤灰就可以大陸判七年<br />\n<br />\n之後就可以光明正大捉你返去坐呀"},{"pid":"dda1bd6acf7ed66d6e67fcd57931